{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"choose","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/XSLT/Element/choose","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n</p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">Dokumentacja XSLT/XPath</a></b>: <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">Elementy XSLT</a>, <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/EXSLT\">Funkcje EXSLT</a>, <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">Funkcje XPath</a>, <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">Osie XPath</a>\n</div>\n<p></p><p>Element <code>&lt;xsl:choose&gt;</code> definiuje wybór spośród określonej liczby wyborów alternatywnych. Przypomina w działaniu wyrażenie switch znane z proceduralnych języków programowania.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":" Składnia ","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;xsl:choose&gt;\n\t&lt;xsl:when test=\"[cokolwiek do sprawdzenia1]\"&gt;&lt;/xsl:when&gt;\n\t&lt;xsl:when test=\"[cokolwiek do sprawdzenia2]\"&gt;&lt;/xsl:when&gt;\n     &lt;xsl:otherwise&gt;&lt;/xsl:otherwise&gt; [opcjonalnie]\n&lt;/xsl:choose&gt;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wymagane_atrybuty","title":" Wymagane atrybuty ","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Brak.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"opcjonalne_atrybuty","title":" Opcjonalne atrybuty ","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Brak.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"typ","title":" Typ ","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Instrukcja. Pojawia się wraz z szablonem. Zawiera jeden lub więcej elementów <code>&lt;xsl:when&gt;</code> i opcjonalnie końcowy element <code>&lt;xsl:otherwise&gt;</code>.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"definicja","title":" Definicja ","isH3":true,"content":"<p>XSLT, sekcja 9.2.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko","title":" Gecko ","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Obsługuje.\n</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Element <xsl:choose> definiuje wybór spośród określonej liczby wyborów alternatywnych. Przypomina w działaniu wyrażenie switch znane z proceduralnych języków programowania.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<xsl:choose>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"choose","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"choose","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<xsl:choose>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"choose","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/xslt/element/choose","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/xslt/element/choose/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/XSLT","title":"XSLT"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/XSLT/Element","title":"Elementy"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/XSLT/Element/choose","title":"choose"}],"pageTitle":"choose - XSLT | MDN","noIndexing":false}}